               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17400709-25-off129-c182" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400709-25-defend231 t17400709-25-off129 t17400709-25-verdict132"></join>
         
               <p>315. 
               
                  <persName id="t17400709-25-defend231" type="defendantName">
                     James 
                     Waldron 
                  <interp inst="t17400709-25-defend231" type="surname" value="Waldron"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-defend231" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-defend231" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , of <placeName id="t17400709-25-defloc128">St Lawrence Jewry</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17400709-25-defloc128" type="placeName" value="St Lawrence Jewry"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17400709-25-defloc128" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400709-25-defend231 t17400709-25-defloc128"></join> , was indicted for <rs id="t17400709-25-off129" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-off129" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-off129" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pettyLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a Pair of turn'd Leather Pumps, val.10 d.
            </rs> the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17400709-25-victim233" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Hose 
                  <interp inst="t17400709-25-victim233" type="surname" value="Hose"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-victim233" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-victim233" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400709-25-off129 t17400709-25-victim233"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17400709-25-cd130" type="crimeDate">June 28</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400709-25-off129 t17400709-25-cd130"></join>.</p>
               <p>Mr Hose . Last Saturday was se'nnight, about half an Hour after 8 at Night, I had a Customer or two in my Shop,(I live in <placeName id="t17400709-25-crimeloc131">Cheapside</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17400709-25-crimeloc131" type="placeName" value="Cheapside"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17400709-25-crimeloc131" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400709-25-off129 t17400709-25-crimeloc131"></join>) and a little Girl cry'd out - Mr Hose, a Man has got a Pair of Pumps. I being lame, could not run after him; but my People pursued him, and took him in Bow Church Yard, and told me he had dropped the Pumps, by the Corner of the Church Yard. When he was brought to my Shop, he fell down on his Knees, begg'd Mercy, and desired I would let the People pump him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I know nothing of the Pumps; I touch'd no Pumps.</p>


               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17400709-25-person234">
                  Cornelia 
                  Harrison 
               <interp inst="t17400709-25-person234" type="surname" value="Harrison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-person234" type="given" value="Cornelia"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-person234" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             , 
               <persName id="t17400709-25-person235">
                  Sarah 
                  Smallwood 
               <interp inst="t17400709-25-person235" type="surname" value="Smallwood"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-person235" type="given" value="Sarah"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-person235" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , and 
               <persName id="t17400709-25-person236">
                  Roger 
                  Lewis 
               <interp inst="t17400709-25-person236" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-person236" type="given" value="Roger"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-person236" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , never knew him do such a Thing in their Lives. The Jury <rs id="t17400709-25-verdict132" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17400709-25-verdict132" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               acquitted
            </rs> him.</p>
            </div1>
